album.title: Music From The Motion Picture Cadillac Records

wiki.content:
this song is originally by Etta James. the song talks about a girl that basically would rather go blind than to see her man walk away from her with another girl. beyonce played as Etta James in the film Cadillac Records and she did a great job!!! which is where beyonces version of this song comes from.

track.name: I'd Rather Go Blind
